## 2. AI Agent with Outlook Calendar Tools
[Learn more about the AI Agent node]({{ $env.WEBHOOK_URL }}

This agent has 3 Outlook tools to search, browse and even create calendar events for the user. Agents are great in that we don't have to tell the agent what and when to use the tools - it'll make that decision on its own!

## 3. Reply to User
[Learn more about the Slack node]({{ $env.WEBHOOK_URL }}

Simple sends a reply back to the user answering their query. Of course, this is the simplest case and it'll be up to you to handle multi-turn conversation as needed.
